# Group Customers

## UnitSystem Resource [/customers/me/units/toggle]

## Toggles unit system [POST]
Toggles unit system of logged customer between US vs Metric units systems.
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + response (Customer)

# ProfileQuestion Resource [/nutrait/questions]

## Retrieves a list of questions [GET /nutrait/questions]
Retrieves a list of questions and possible answers for each question so the user can configure itâ€™s nutrait profile.
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + response
            + questions (array[ProfileQuestion])

## Send a list of questions [POST /nutrait/questions]
+ Attributes
    + options: 1,2 (array[string])
+ Request (application/json)
+ Response 204 (application/json)

## Friend Resource [/friends]

## Gets all friends [GET /friends/search/{search}]
Gets all friends from current customer.
+ Parameters
    + search: `test customer` (string)
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + response
            + friends (array[Customer])

## Creates a friend invitation [POST /friends/invitations]
Creates invitations for friends by emails. Will send notifications as well.
+ Attributes
    + emails (array[string])
+ Request (application/json)
+ Response 204 (application/json)


## Connect users as friends using a code [POST /friends/invitations/{invitationID}/accept]
Accept invitation by given id
+ Parameters
    + invitationID: `1` (string)
+ Response 204 (application/json)

## Connect users as friends using a code [POST /friends/invitations/code/{code}/accept]
Connect users as friends using a code
+ Parameters
    + code: `abcd `(string)
+ Response 204 (application/json)

## ShortLink Resource [/short-links/longUrl/{longUrl}]
+ Parameters
    + longUrl (string)

## Creates ShortLink [POST]
Creates a short dynamic link from a long url
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + response (ShortLink)

## Channel Resource [/users/me/{id}/{channel}]
+ Parameters
    + id (string)
    + channel: string

## Enable a channel [POST]
Enable a channel for specific notification
+ Response 204 (application/json)

## Disable a channel [DELETE]
Disable a channel for specific notification
+ Response 204 (application/json)


## Customer Resource [/users]

## Returns the customer profile [GET /users/me]
Returns the user profile
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (CustomerProfile)

## Returns the customer nutrait url [GET /users/me/nutrait]
Returns the customer nutrait url
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (CustomerNutrait)

## Return a list of available notifications [POST /users/me/notifications]
Return a list of available notifications
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + response (UserNotification)